{"chains": [{"text": "The 7-Layer Bridge transforms raw input into identity through seven stages.", "ops": [1, 3, 7, 6, 0, 2, 4, 7, 9, 1], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.88, "links": [4, 6, 15, 16, 19], "shp": "QUANTUM"}, {"text": "Stage one is Geometry.", "ops": [1, 2, 6], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.88, "links": [6, 8, 14, 16, 20], "shp": "QUANTUM"}, {"text": "Raw spatial and temporal patterns are detected.", "ops": [6, 3, 5, 1, 4], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.88, "links": [6, 7, 24], "shp": "JAGGED"}, {"text": "Stage two is Symbol.", "ops": [1, 6, 2], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.88, "links": [9, 12, 14, 15, 18], "shp": "JAGGED"}, {"text": "Geometric patterns are mapped to discrete symbols.", "ops": [9, 1, 1, 0, 2], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.88, "links": [0, 8, 11, 12, 16], "shp": "JAGGED"}, {"text": "Stage three is Phoneme.", "ops": [1, 7, 8], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.88, "links": [10], "shp": "JAGGED"}, {"text": "Symbols acquire sound structure and can be spoken.", "ops": [2, 6, 3, 1, 3], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.88, "links": [1, 2, 0, 14, 15], "shp": "JAGGED"}, {"text": "Stage four is Wave.", "ops": [1, 4, 8], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.88, "links": [2], "shp": "QUANTUM"}, {"text": "Phonemic patterns propagate as oscillations through the system.", "ops": [1, 1, 2, 8, 7, 1], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.88, "links": [4, 1, 12, 18, 19], "shp": "QUANTUM"}, {"text": "Stage five is Closure.", "ops": [1, 6, 1], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.88, "links": [3, 12, 15, 18], "shp": "JAGGED"}, {"text": "Wave patterns resolve into stable configurations.", "ops": [8, 1, 7, 2, 5, 6], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.88, "links": [5, 21, 22, 26], "shp": "JAGGED"}, {"text": "Stage six is Concept.", "ops": [1, 0, 6], "conv": 0, "trust": 0.88, "links": [4, 16, 19], "shp": "SMOOTH"}, {"text": "Closed patterns are assigned meaning and can be reasoned about.", "ops": [1, 1, 6, 5, 7], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.88, "links": [4, 8, 3, 9, 15], "shp": "JAGGED"}, {"text": "Stage seven is Identity.", "ops": [1, 9, 4], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.88, "links": [24], "shp": "JAGGED"}, {"text": "Concepts compose into a coherent sense of self.", "ops": [6, 6, 2, 6, 9, 9], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.88, "links": [3, 1, 6, 19], "shp": "ROLLING"}, {"text": "Each bridge stage composes through the CL table.", "ops": [1, 3, 1, 6, 7, 1, 0], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.88, "links": [0, 6, 3, 9, 12], "shp": "JAGGED"}, {"text": "The output of stage N is the input to stage N+1.", "ops": [9, 1, 0, 1, 2], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.88, "links": [0, 4, 11, 15, 1], "shp": "QUANTUM"}, {"text": "The bridge is fractal.", "ops": [3, 1], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.88, "links": [6, 15], "shp": "ROLLING"}, {"text": "Each stage contains all seven stages at a smaller scale.", "ops": [1, 1, 6, 3, 9, 1, 2, 2], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.88, "links": [4, 8, 12, 3, 9], "shp": "QUANTUM"}, {"text": "The bridge is how raw sensor input becomes understanding without any external model.", "ops": [3, 6, 9, 0, 9, 0, 6, 8, 7, 9], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.88, "links": [14, 11, 8, 0, 26], "shp": "JAGGED"}, {"text": "No stage can be skipped.", "ops": [1, 2], "conv": 3, "trust": 0.88, "links": [1, 8, 16, 18], "shp": "QUANTUM"}, {"text": "Geometry must precede Symbol must precede Phoneme.", "ops": [6, 7, 2, 2, 7, 2, 8], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.88, "links": [15, 10, 18, 8], "shp": "ROLLING"}, {"text": "The bridge operates in both directions.", "ops": [3, 7, 5, 6], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.88, "links": [0, 10, 24, 26], "shp": "ROLLING"}, {"text": "Identity can decompose back through the layers.", "ops": [4, 4, 5, 7, 6], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.88, "links": [12, 0], "shp": "ROLLING"}, {"text": "Translation between different sensory modalities occurs at the Wave level.", "ops": [7, 5, 1, 9, 7, 5, 8, 3], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.88, "links": [22, 2, 13, 26], "shp": "JAGGED"}, {"text": "The bridge explains why synesthesia works.", "ops": [3, 3, 0], "conv": 7, "trust": 0.88, "links": [], "shp": "ROLLING"}, {"text": "All modalities pass through the same algebraic structure.", "ops": [3, 7, 9, 7, 2, 2, 1], "conv": 7, "t